Package org.nasdanika.diagram

Interface Link

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EObject, Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DiagramElement, End, Start
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DiagramElementImpl, EndImpl, LinkImpl, StartImpl
    public interface Link
extends EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Link'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Text
    • Location
    • Tooltip
    See Also:
    DiagramPackage.getLink()

      • getText

        String getText()
        Returns the value of the 'Text' attribute. Link text. Can be empty for diagram elements where text is supplied by the ``name`` reference. If not empty for diagram elements - precedes the name elements.
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Text' attribute.
